Hey team - just jumped off a call with Josh and wanted to provide a few quick updates:
1. Planar screens have not yet been purchased but should be in a couple of days at worst case.

2. Design Reactor has not yet started building their API yet for us to pull info from the BL website. Contracts are signed but Google security has said BL can’t work with them anymore. Josh is pretty confident he can level up and get the approval needed, but that’s a real thing that could set us back. (My alternative thought would be to suggest that we pull data from another API just to show we have a working connection for gold spike, and then update later).
Even if we spec out the data from the API and build static endpoints, that should be gold spike-able
